153
00:05:10,340 --> 00:05:11,420
- Yeah? - It turned into a reef!

154
00:05:11,430 --> 00:05:13,030
That's 'cause you left your door cracked open!

155
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:14,000
Yes, it was my fault.

156
